<title>USA: Management Technologies names Edison CEO.</title>
<headline>Management Technologies names Edison CEO.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-02-11</dateline>
<text>
<p>Management Technologies Inc of London said on Tuesday it has brought in Michael Edison as chief executive, replacing Paul Ekon.</p>
<p>Edison, 51, mostly recently headed Edison Management Co, a private investment company. He also was made a director of Management Technologies, a financial-services software supplier.</p>
